movie_title: Star Wars: Episode I - The Phantom Menace
title: Wow! Experience!
review: Star Wars I: the Phantom Menace is excellent. Not the plot, but all the great special effects makes this movie a real EXPERIENCE. And Darth Maul is so damn cool with his two-bladed laser sword. 'At last we will reveal ourselves to the Jedi. At last we will have revenge.'
